==Japanese==
===Etymology===
{{ja-kanjitab-top}}
! [[一]] || [[ヶ]] || [[月]]
{{ja-kanjitab-bottom}}
[[一]] (いち, ''ichi''), "one" + [[ヶ]], a simplified form of [[箇]] (か, ''ka''), the counter for months + [[月]] (がつ, ''gatsu''), "month"

===Noun===
'''一ヶ月''' ([[いっかげつ]], ''ikkagetsu'')

# [[一箇月]]: one month (duration)

